{"tid":1940792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強宣布中國全國本土肺炎疫情傳播已基本阻斷，抗疫獲得初步成功","createTime":"2020-03-24T04:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T12:45:26.000Z","uid":155095,"like":62,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"6af2eb634babf2a9c26301ed0245f030b924e0ea","tid":1940792,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"中國國務院總理、中央應對新冠肺炎疫情工作領導小組組長<strong>李克強</strong>23日宣告，「當前，以武漢市為主戰場的全國本土疫情傳播已基本阻斷。」這是<del>新冠肺炎</del><ins>武漢肺炎</ins>疫情自去年12月檢測發現後，感染肆虐逾三個月以來，大陸官方首度正式表態，抗疫獲得初步成功。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>李克強</strong>23日召開中央應對新冠肺炎疫情工作領導小組會議，正式宣告以武漢市為主戰場的全國本土疫情傳播已基本阻斷。不過，他表示，零星散發病例和局部暴發疫情的風險仍然存在，疫情在全球出現大流行，形勢依然復雜嚴峻，要保持清醒頭腦，決不可掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/03/23/realtime/7637426.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=930&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F03%2F23%2Frealtime%2F7637426.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D930%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465%26nt%3D1&h=febb5277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>李克強</strong>要求，要實行「外防輸入、內防反彈」的總體防控策略，維護好來之不易的防控成果。<br />\n<br />\n針對武漢防疫，<strong>李克強</strong>表示，武漢市和湖北省要緊緊扭住醫療救治和社區防控兩個關鍵環節，繼續做好重症患者救治，及時收治新發病例，並做好流行病學調查。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，各地要堅持實事求是、公開透明發布信息，不得瞞報漏報。一旦發現疫情要實行精準管控，聚焦在病例發生和可能傳播的場所，控制在有限範圍。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120936/4437898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120936%2F4437898&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=4e14df81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120936/4437898</a>"},{"pid":"5fb4711becae1b6cd17b2d29bc4e3b61027d587e","tid":1940792,"uid":53003,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"復工啦快"},{"pid":"41e4f6ea32393c6e65e2d72e1294e72595ae3849","tid":1940792,"uid":249794,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"重點係有冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d19f8ad1da5617974f888de6280d66b18b6313","tid":1940792,"uid":222140,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"見支那疫情好似有復甦跡象<br />\n<br />\n同理, 全世界都唔得閒要你啲產品, <br />\n<br />\n復工返去冇單接開咩工咩"},{"pid":"fbd0a7432009e06e3a95adaa0f3b2984b95d9aba","tid":1940792,"uid":338097,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"叫俄佬同北韓快d解封"},{"pid":"d4e76a68cc2d88acf9ef33c0b9e6f836b43f60dd","tid":1940792,"uid":155095,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"fbd0a7432009e06e3a95adaa0f3b2984b95d9aba","tid":1940792,"uid":338097,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"叫俄佬同北韓快d解封"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/0316/20200316100135889.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F0316%2F20200316100135889.png&h=5f6c2fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nm9B2E3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnm9B2E3.jpg&h=607b6369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41cbcb59627026b01f0a75c41bedfcd7cafb47b0","tid":1940792,"uid":85461,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7ror7OuodW8/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F7ror7OuodW8%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=71ab143c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4327d4b47af914b0065e5b1d7f5cb5b6c703631c","tid":1940792,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41e4f6ea32393c6e65e2d72e1294e72595ae3849","tid":1940792,"